<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900725-0119</DOCNO><DOCID>900725-0119.</DOCID><HL>   Dividend News:   Robert Half International Inc.</HL><DATE>07/25/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION</SO><CO>   RHI</CO><IN>DIVIDENDS (DIV)</IN><LP>   ROBERT HALF INTERNATIONAL Inc., Menlo Park, Calif.,instituted an anti-takeover &quot;poison pill,&quot; declaring adividend of one preferred share purchase right for each shareof common stock. The dividend will be payable Aug. 8 to stockof record on that date. The rights will expire Aug. 8, 2000.The terms of the rights are activated only if 30% or more ofthe company's stock is acquired by a person or group. In theevent of a sale or merger, the holder is entitled to purchasestock in the acquiring company at half the market price.Robert Half International specializes in the placement oftax, banking and financial personnel services.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>